{
  "id": "RAW_aa7c6b7c",
  "title": "始末｜Cursor 爆火的自研模型，是 Kimi K2.5，创始人说「下次会改」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&mid=2247514525&idx=1&sn=9f965a129363d0120596dddb8cef2ede",
  "date": "2026-03-21 04:56:00",
  "author": "赛博禅心",
  "siteName": "赛博禅心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"padding:0;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:24px 16px 32px;\">\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">子曰：国内一开源，海外就自研</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">估值 500 亿美金的 Cursor，刚发布了号称「自研前沿模型」的 Composer 2。不到 24 小时，一个开发者在调试 API 的时候发现：</span><strong style=\"color:#c23616;font-weight:700;\"><span leaf=\"\">它的 model ID 里直接写着 kimi-k2p5</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi K2.5，Moonshot AI 的开源模型。Cursor 拿来跑了一遍 RL，博客里通篇写的「our model」，一个字没提，这就....哈哈哈哈哈哈</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">一个 model ID，扒掉了「自研」外衣</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">3月19日 Cursor 发布 Composer 2。同日，开发者 @fynnso 在调试 Cursor 的 OpenAI 兼容 base URL 时，返回的模型列表里出现了这一行：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"border:1px solid #e5e4e0;border-radius:6px;padding:12px 16px;margin:0 0 14px;\"><code style=\"word-break:break-all;font-size:13px;font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;line-height:1.6;\"><span leaf=\"\">accounts/anysphere/models/kimi-k2p5-rl-0317-s515-fast</span></code></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">他发了条推：「so composer 2 is just Kimi K2.5 with RL. at least rename the model ID」</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">截止本文发出时，已经 230 万浏览了</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.040169133192389\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"946\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdhVrpjr8woMhKFHNBhmYevSgXmWtiajqWfrVVpc6XRVTQ3KPVrykYMUlakgicnEVDw4P2UR2mu2tibqGLu8uvC8icBrH9jsEysZSLk/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"845\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"568\" data-imgfileid=\"100030867\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9737df0b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdhVrpjr8woMhKFHNBhmYevSgXmWtiajqWfrVVpc6XRVTQ3KPVrykYMUlakgicnEVDw4P2UR2mu2tibqGLu8uvC8icBrH9jsEysZSLk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">fynnso 的推文，引爆了整件事</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个 model ID 里的信息量，连猜都不用猜：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #e5e4e0;border-radius:8px;padding:20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;color:#c23616;\"><span leaf=\"\">kimi-k2p5</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;→ Kimi K2.5</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;color:#c23616;\"><span leaf=\"\">rl</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;→ 强化学习</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;color:#c23616;\"><span leaf=\"\">0317</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;→ 3月17日的版本（发布前两天）</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;color:#c23616;\"><span leaf=\"\">s515</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;→ 大概率是某个 RL seed 编号</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;color:#c23616;\"><span leaf=\"\">fast</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;→ 推理加速版本</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 用了 Kimi K2.5 做基座，跑了一遍 RL 微调，连模型标识符都没改掉</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">→ 原始推文：x.com/fynnso/status/2034706304875602030</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 的官方博客怎么写的</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">回头看 Cursor 的发布博客，号称在 Terminal-Bench 2.0 上得分 61.7，超过 Claude Opus 4.6 的 58.0，定价还便宜一大截（$0.50/M input，$2.50/M output）</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">用的措辞是「our first continued pretraining run, which provides a far stronger base to scale our reinforcement learning」，自研基座 + 强化学习，正经的前沿模型叙事</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"color:#c23616;font-weight:700;\"><span leaf=\"\">全文没有出现 Kimi、Moonshot、或【任何第三方模型】的名字，通篇【our model】</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1903973509933774\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1208\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdjHGeDnJF69UIrRH70lY4R4Y55P1MbePuDaagjKD5URX9rKqUUicibdwG8JU4Arz0JcbvHYuPrcE3GJEY7S0aapX4pjRk9ETHelU/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"650\" data-imgfileid=\"100030866\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ced06e2c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdjHGeDnJF69UIrRH70lY4R4Y55P1MbePuDaagjKD5URX9rKqUUicibdwG8JU4Arz0JcbvHYuPrcE3GJEY7S0aapX4pjRk9ETHelU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor Composer 2 官方博客，通篇「our model」</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">→ Cursor 官方博客：cursor.com/blog/composer-2</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi K2.5 这个模型</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">作为背景，让我们先回顾下 Kimi K2.5：<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&amp;mid=2247511844&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=c94ef04e001a01ce3a2dd6614700dc3f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"K2.5，是 Kimi 的一个分水岭\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">K2.5，是 Kimi 的一个分水岭</a></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是 Moonshot 今年新发布的模型，支持原生多模态，支持 256K 上下文窗口，能自主调度最多 100 个子 Agent 的 Swarm 协作</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 coding 领域，K2.5 已经是开源模型里的天花板：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #e5e4e0;border-radius:8px;padding:20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">65.8</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;SWE-bench Verified&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#8a8a82;font-size:13px;\"><span leaf=\"\">pass@1</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，开源最高</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">47.3</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;SWE-bench Multilingual，开源最高</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">53.7</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;LiveCodeBench v6，开源最高</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">前端开发能力尤其突出，从一段对话直接生成完整的交互式界面</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#c23616;line-height:1.9;margin:0;text-align:center;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">全球最贵的 AI 编程工具选它当基座，技术水平到这了</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">→ Kimi K2.5 技术博客：kimi.com/blog/kimi-k2-5</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">许可证怎么写的，Cursor 的数字是多少</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi K2.5 用的是 Modified MIT License，原文公开在 HuggingFace 上</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心条款有这么一段：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果使用 Kimi K2.5（包括衍生作品）的商业产品，月活用户超过 1 亿或月收入超过 2000 万美元，必须在产品的用户界面上显著展示「Kimi K2.5」</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 的数据：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #e5e4e0;border-radius:8px;padding:20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">ARR 超过 20 亿美元</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">（2026年2月数据），月均约&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"color:#c23616;font-weight:700;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.67 亿美元</span></strong></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"color:#c23616;font-weight:700;\"><span leaf=\"\">超过许可证触发门槛约 8 倍</span></strong></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">日活用户超过 100 万</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">最新估值 293 亿美元，正在谈 500 亿美金的下一轮</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 的 UI 上写的是「Composer 2」，没有 Kimi 的任何字样</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">→ 许可证原文：huggingface.co/moonshotai/Kimi-K2.5/blob/main/LICENSE</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 怎么回的</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">两个人出来说话</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">先是 Cursor 的 Lee Robinson 发了两条推</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一条：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;border-left:3px solid #c23616;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Yep, Composer 2 started from an open-source base! We will do full pretraining in the future. Only ~1/4 of the compute spent on the final model came from the base, the rest is from our training</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">（是的，Composer 2 从一个开源基座开始训练的。未来我们会做完整的从头预训练。最终模型只有约 1/4 的算力来自基座，剩下的都是我们自己的训练）</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.547568710359408\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"946\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdiaC0rI7bxEOf4LE6ibvfNPE7AYGvcqw7EdBN8qQsnuVhicuBYiaPY3DSMMh72DyTo4FwyWNUH4d17vV7ia08Kfz7ujjic612dUt4IwE/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"574\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"845\" data-imgfileid=\"100030869\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=74eaa9e3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdiaC0rI7bxEOf4LE6ibvfNPE7AYGvcqw7EdBN8qQsnuVhicuBYiaPY3DSMMh72DyTo4FwyWNUH4d17vV7ia08Kfz7ujjic612dUt4IwE%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二条更直接：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;border-left:3px solid #c23616;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Since people really want me to say this: \"KIMI K2.5\" ‼️ Yes, that is the base we started from. And we are following the license through inference partner terms (e.g. Fireworks)</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">（既然大家这么想听我说这个：「KIMI K2.5」‼️ 是的，这就是我们的起点基座。我们通过推理合作方的条款在遵守许可证，比如 Fireworks）</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5348837209302325\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"946\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdiaUFF17Ns5NgC6LtOYABbRDx3PTOTeXoCJAXSfMEias0icFJ9FlcUxVUs6vibf7SUoicKDJDUVwF9T2EXY8AMYuatUdrN8ZVtpZMYw/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"845\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"292\" data-imgfileid=\"100030868\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=795f1201&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdiaUFF17Ns5NgC6LtOYABbRDx3PTOTeXoCJAXSfMEias0icFJ9FlcUxVUs6vibf7SUoicKDJDUVwF9T2EXY8AMYuatUdrN8ZVtpZMYw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后 Cursor 的创始人，Aman Sanger 也正式回应了：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;border-left:3px solid #c23616;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">We've evaluated a lot of base models on perplexity-based evals and&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px 6px 6px 0px;max-width:640px;color:rgb(194, 54, 22);word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\">Kimi k2.5 proved to be the strongest!</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;After that, we do continued pre-training and high-compute RL (a 4x scale-up). The combination of the strong base, CPT and RL, and Fireworks' inference and RL samplers make Composer-2 frontier level</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px 6px 6px 0px;max-width:640px;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">.&nbsp;</span></span><strong style=\"border-radius:0px 6px 6px 0px;max-width:640px;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">It was a miss to not mention the Kimi base in our blog from the start.&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"color:#c23616;font-weight:700;\"><span leaf=\"\">We'll fix that for the next model.</span></strong></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"color:#c23616;font-weight:700;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px 6px 6px 0px;max-width:640px;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">（我们用 perplexity 指标评估了大量基座模型，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px 6px 6px 0px;max-width:640px;color:rgb(194, 54, 22);word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\">Kimi K2.5 是最强的</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px 6px 6px 0px;max-width:640px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。在此基础上我们做了继续预训练和大算力 RL（4 倍规模扩展）。强基座 + CPT + RL + Fireworks 的推理和 RL 采样器，这些组合让 Composer 2 达到了前沿水平</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px 6px 6px 0px;max-width:640px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px 6px 6px 0px;max-width:640px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;博客里没有提到 Kimi 基座，是我们的失误。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">下一个模型我们会改&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"border-radius:0px 6px 6px 0px;max-width:640px;word-break:break-all;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;font-family:&quot;Noto Sans SC&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">）</span></span></strong></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9978858350951374\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"946\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdh9yxHqKUstV3K5ovQNopMjhKwssbP2iaO7P7TXtLoYJw4f1gkR1hMeNUj7J5iba68LPOHWtHahcPsOKrJ66beMpKePZe4DASb3U/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"934\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"545\" data-imgfileid=\"100030876\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8b4fc1eb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdh9yxHqKUstV3K5ovQNopMjhKwssbP2iaO7P7TXtLoYJw4f1gkR1hMeNUj7J5iba68LPOHWtHahcPsOKrJ66beMpKePZe4DASb3U%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Aman Sanger 这条信息量比较大：第一，承认 Kimi K2.5 在他们评估的所有基座模型里最强；第二，承认博客没写来源是「a miss」；第三，明确了 Fireworks 在整个链条里的角色，不只是推理，还提供 RL 采样器</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">社区的反应基本还是一个问题：既然知道该写，为什么发的时候不写？</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">→ Lee Robinson 推文：x.com/leerob/status/2035050444347600936</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">→ Aman Sanger 推文：x.com/amanrsanger/status/2035079293257359663</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">Moonshot 的回应很「硬」</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Moonshot 官方账号 @Kimi_Moonshot 最后出来说了话：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"border-radius:0 6px 6px 0;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;border-left:3px solid #c23616;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Congrats to the @cursor_ai team on the launch of Composer 2!</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span leaf=\"\">We are proud to see Kimi-k2.5 provide the foundation. Seeing our model integrated effectively through Cursor's continued pretraining &amp; high-compute RL training is the open model ecosystem we love to support.</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span leaf=\"\">Note: Cursor accesses Kimi-k2.5 via @FireworksAI_HQ hosted RL and inference platform as part of an authorized commercial partnership.</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">一条推文四层信息：</span></p>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #e5e4e0;border-radius:8px;padding:20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">1. 祝贺（场面话）</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">2. 「We are proud to see Kimi-k2.5 provide the foundation」，当着所有人的面</span><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">确认了基座归属</span></strong></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">3. 肯定 Cursor 的训练投入（给了台阶）</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">4. 点名 Fireworks AI 作为中间方，用了「authorized commercial partnership」，有合同，钱到位了</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6109936575052854\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"946\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdh8555Dukafic68NgTOjBfJmBs1pYaib09WtfCEAchiasKuPDnBgHe5p5XItsj4L5pGLgreibChJ0RuVFGILdRVgy9pzUmsHERFaC0/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"545\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"334\" data-imgfileid=\"100030870\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9af12f92&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdh8555Dukafic68NgTOjBfJmBs1pYaib09WtfCEAchiasKuPDnBgHe5p5XItsj4L5pGLgreibChJ0RuVFGILdRVgy9pzUmsHERFaC0%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">我是觉得，这个推文写的很有水平：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">整体姿态大方，每个关键事实都钉住了，又没追着打，该确认的技术归属确认了，场面上还给足了体面</span></p>\n    <div style=\"border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:#c23616;line-height:1.9;margin:0;text-align:center;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi K2.5 的技术够硬，Moonshot 的态度也够硬</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">→ Moonshot 官方推文：x.com/Kimi_Moonshot/status/2035074972943831491</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">→ Simon Willison 的收录：simonwillison.net/2026/Mar/20/cursor-on-kimi/</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">前史：去年 10 月就出过同款乐子</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">这事有前科</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">2025年10月30日，前微软 VS Code 团队成员 Kenneth Auchenberg 在 X 上发推配截图。他在用 Cursor 的 Composer 1 编程时，模型的 chain-of-thought（内心独白）突然切换成了中文，而且切不回来</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0507399577167018\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"946\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdhhZt38nicUcS0Xt7GZciaPTxZozro7SBF86sHtBhzXR1OsHTwDj8dvG6c34zXQ2Nh1PwQoI2OSWSibjIDCHia5YHqR36xZDcWtEMQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"574\" data-imgfileid=\"100030871\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=aa544a37&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdhhZt38nicUcS0Xt7GZciaPTxZozro7SBF86sHtBhzXR1OsHTwDj8dvG6c34zXQ2Nh1PwQoI2OSWSibjIDCHia5YHqR36xZDcWtEMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Auchenberg 的推文，Cursor Composer 1 的内心独白切换成了中文</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">当时 Cursor 的处理方式是不回应，快速迭代到 1.5 版本把话题盖过去。Hacker News 上有人指出，Cursor 的第一代 Composer 也是基于中文开源基座（有说法是 GLM，但目前还没有直接证据）</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次 Composer 2 连 model ID 都没改名，老习惯了</span></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:13px;color:#8a8a82;line-height:1.75;margin:0 0 8px;word-break:break-all;\"><span leaf=\"\">→ 原始推文：x.com/auchenberg/status/1983901551048470974</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">几个可以确认的事实</span></h2>\n    <div style=\"border:1px solid #e5e4e0;border-radius:8px;padding:20px;margin:0 0 14px;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Composer 2 的基座是 Kimi K2.5，Cursor 自己公开承认了</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 在基座之上做了 continued pre-training + RL，声称约 3/4 算力用于后训练</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">3.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Kimi K2.5 的 Modified MIT 许可证对月收入超 2000 万美元的产品有明确的 UI 署名要求</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">4.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 月收入约 1.67 亿美元，超出触发门槛 8 倍，发布时没有任何署名</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">5.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 通过 Fireworks AI 访问 Kimi K2.5 的权重，Moonshot 确认存在授权商业合作</span></p>\n     <p style=\"margin:0 0 0;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">6.</span></span><span leaf=\"\">许可证的署名条款（UI 显著展示「Kimi K2.5」）和推理合作（通过 Fireworks 付费使用）是两件事，目前 Cursor 只做了后者</span></p>\n    </div>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">公开信息到这里为止</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-weight:700;font-size:22px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">其他</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">事件发酵一天之后，一个相对冷静的视角来自 Michael Guo（@Michaelzsguo）,他的判断是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">这本质上就是一次典型乌龙</span>。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fireworks AI 其实早在 21 小时前就已经发布过 Composer 2 的消息，并明确说了这是基于他们基础设施进行 RL 训练的模型。Cursor 的使用是合法的，只是在发布博客的时候玩了个小猫腻，只字不提背后的开源模型，结果给人抓了个小辫子</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">他也梳理了各方的实际得失：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Kimi / Moonshot 是最大赢家</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。几乎零成本拿到了一波全球级别的曝光，带来了几百万浏览和大量讨论，也顺带证明了自己的开源模型已经强到可以被顶级 coding 产品选作底座。和 Fireworks 的合作关系也被进一步放大，海外知名度和生态影响力都上了一个台阶</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:600;\"><span leaf=\"\">Fireworks AI 也明显受益</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。这件事让更多人第一次注意到它，尤其是在开发者圈。大家看到的已经不只是一个 inference provider，而是一家有能力在开源模型之上做全参数 RL tuning 的基础设施公司</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin:0 0 14px;word-break:break-all;font-size:15px;font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.9;\"><span leaf=\"\">至于 Cursor，产品确实好用，Composer 2 的实际体验评价也不错。只是发布时不写来源这件事，在社区里留下了一个不太好的印象</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.7103594080338267\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"946\" style=\"border-radius:6px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/jXSGuwJvpdhdw5ibawwO2HbfSoBAb4TyINyKb7Z3JPBw4pUqM9XLMrzd9yZoytK2QcB07uuPCsoACJvSS2LGHraGhGflnahV3SmSTtnqDyyg/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"934\" data-imgfileid=\"100030875\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=60de7614&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FjXSGuwJvpdhdw5ibawwO2HbfSoBAb4TyINyKb7Z3JPBw4pUqM9XLMrzd9yZoytK2QcB07uuPCsoACJvSS2LGHraGhGflnahV3SmSTtnqDyyg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n    <p style=\"font-family:'Noto Sans SC','PingFang SC','Microsoft YaHei',-apple-system,sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;text-align:center;margin:0 0 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://x.com/Michaelzsguo/status/2035102518552707261\" target=\"_blank\">https://x.com/Michaelzsguo/status/2035102518552707261</a></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;padding:32px 16px;\">\n    <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 14px;font-weight:600;font-size:18px;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','Songti SC',STSong,Georgia,serif;line-height:1.4;\"><span leaf=\"\">所有一手出处</span></h3>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Cursor 官方博客</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">cursor.com/blog/composer-2</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">@fynnso 发现 model ID</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">x.com/fynnso/status/2034706304875602030</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Lee Robinson 确认基座</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">x.com/leerob/status/2035050444347600936</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Aman Sanger 正式回应</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">x.com/amanrsanger/status/2035079293257359663</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Moonshot 官方回应</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">x.com/Kimi_Moonshot/status/2035074972943831491</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Kimi K2.5 许可证原文</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">huggingface.co/moonshotai/Kimi-K2.5/blob/main/LICENSE</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Kenneth Auchenberg 去年10月推文</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">x.com/auchenberg/status/1983901551048470974</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Michael Guo 事件复盘</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">x.com/Michaelzsguo/status/2035102518552707261</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Simon Willison 收录</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">simonwillison.net/2026/Mar/20/cursor-on-kimi/</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Hacker News 讨论帖</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">news.ycombinator.com/item?id=47452404</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;\">\n     <p style=\"margin:0;word-break:break-all;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;\"><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:13px;color:#c23616;margin-right:8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">→</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Recording Law 法律分析</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n       <br> \n      </span><span style=\"font-family:'JetBrains Mono','SF Mono',Menlo,Consolas,monospace;font-size:12px;color:#8a8a82;\"><span leaf=\"\">recordinglaw.com/what-model-is-cursor-2-kimi-k2-5/</span></span></p>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"padding:8px 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e5e4e0;